{"word":"H1082 - בָּלַג - bâlag - baw-lag' - Comfort","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">בָּלַג</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>bâlag"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>baw-lag'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Comfort"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - திடன்கொள், பலத்தல், சந்தோஷமாக இரு, களி கூரு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to gleam, to smile (Hiphil), to show a smile, to look pleasant, to cause to burst"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; to <i>break off</i> or <i>loose</i> (in a favorable or unfavorable sense), that is, <i>desist</i> (from grief) or <i>invade</i> (with destruction): - comfort, (recover) strength(-en)."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1082 - בָּלַג - bâlag - baw-lag'/1082\">H1082</a>, <a href=\"#/H1083 - בִּלְגַה - Bilgah - bil-gaw'/1083\">H1083</a>, <a href=\"#/H1084 - בִּלְגַּי - Bilgay - bil-gah'ee/1084\">H1084</a>, <a href=\"#/H1085 - בִּלְדַּד - Bildad - bil-dad'/1085\">H1085</a>, <a href=\"#/H1088 - בָּלָה - Bâlâh - baw-law'/1088\">H1088</a>, <a href=\"#/H4010 - מַבְלִיגִית - mablîygîyth - mab-leeg-eeth'/4010\">H4010</a>"}]}